txt.en: 'The Rangers have located the morvul they believe to be in charge of the merrevail forces here in the Circle of Madness. He would be a formidable opponent. Would you be willing to challenge him while you are exploring this tier of the city?'
The Rangers have identified the merrevail captain in the Circle of Madness, and have asked for your help defeating him.
'The deed is done? Thank you, [placeholder]. The Rangers are fortunate to have you as an ally.'
Captain Hethulos can be found somewhere in the Circle of Madness.\n\nYou should defeat Captain Hethulos.
Dolenthol is stationed inside Barad Elenath, the Star-gazers' Spire.\n\nYou should talk to Dolenthol.
